Fake SMTP server to relay any message to a specific mail account via a
specific MTA.

Usage:

  $ perl resmtp.pl \
    [-d|--daemon] \
    [-h|--host <listen_host>] \
    [-p|--port <listen_port>] \
    [-t|--timeout <timeout_in_seconds>] \
    [-b|--blackhole] \
    [-f|--from <smtp.mail.from@example.net>] \
    <recipient@example.net> [<smtp_host[:port]>]

